{"tid":367484,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"初試煎牛扒","createTime":"2017-08-20T18:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T16:46:55.000Z","uid":11477,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b42d53de5e873b621ccba3413b12077a31b2a345","tid":367484,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"最近好多煎扒post<br />\n所以一直蠢蠢欲動<br />\n到琴日去一田買左兩塊<br />\n一塊紐西蘭西冷一塊美國安格斯肉眼<br />\n肉眼係個啲即簡即磅到買<br />\n西冷係pack好咁賣<br />\n埋單兩塊$180<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/014915_28cc4884f707589e7ca5ff65f77b0060.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F014915_28cc4884f707589e7ca5ff65f77b0060.jpg&h=f216f6f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地買埋香草 黑胡椒 海鹽 同黃芥辣 牛油自己有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先唔理三七廿一我地係咁隊啲黑胡椒上去<br />\n因為第一次煮唔知要幾多<br />\n我地之前追post話唔好落鹽因爲會搶哂啲水份所以就無落鹽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/015014_43720a64e39610628259684f5c2c2b2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F015014_43720a64e39610628259684f5c2c2b2c.jpg&h=c8f9895b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後撻爐煮啦 <br />\n點知好似有少少燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢塊西冷每邊兩分鐘最尾仲會煎煎佢個油脂邊邊位<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/015242_7e2c30c286909fea2ac26caf71ad8023.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F015242_7e2c30c286909fea2ac26caf71ad8023.jpg&h=dc8afcc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/015243_7e2c30c286909fea2ac26caf71ad8023.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F015243_7e2c30c286909fea2ac26caf71ad8023.jpg&h=349d6c62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地都唔知係咪咁煎就鳩dum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢塊就每邊三分鐘<br />\n最後三十秒就屌埋舊牛油落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/015508_9f1048ef37cbb83bda81e2727e4bf470.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F015508_9f1048ef37cbb83bda81e2727e4bf470.jpg&h=94f96798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上碟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地兩個見到咁燶覺得一定煮過頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/015627_2743eb3ce6c7cb4d847a8543fc3f2afe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F015627_2743eb3ce6c7cb4d847a8543fc3f2afe.jpg&h=aa297204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點知切開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肉眼有三成<br />\n因為同緊我老母食男朋友唔敢玩電話所以影一張就無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/015730_087b15785551166452c917e5b1343f49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F015730_087b15785551166452c917e5b1343f49.jpg&h=ab00dcae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有無牛扒高手有更多技巧啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如點樣知道要煎幾耐<br />\n我地今次都係鳩估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216772ad4a86f86c61b205aa52c7d3a28c8c79fe","tid":367484,"uid":15814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:04:34.000Z","msg":"雖然好似好撚燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但切開好似又唔錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留名睇連登大廚評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0501ecbd779072c666e3884bef122616d823845e","tid":367484,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然好似好撚燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但切開好似又唔錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留名睇連登大廚評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反開個下都呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗點解咁燶大火咁煎應該無錯啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩入面唔係熟哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e16bcf4bbd2cc4d90d1f76f74d1bec571fa62b2","tid":367484,"uid":100099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:18:28.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁多蒜同香草呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實可以落鹽，但一落鹽完就要落鑊"},{"pid":"7b8a55d3c0e065233e5a54474ed7df305a6db9be","tid":367484,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:19:49.000Z","msg":"同緊老母食男朋友？"},{"pid":"c62336694077a65bd2fcb90040c91500bf344198","tid":367484,"uid":15580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"下次個火可以細返少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580866d5dd903f5ad49bbc684c7a4f403e2d0816","tid":367484,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:22:06.000Z","msg":"唔曳喎，外面少少燶仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3283a39fa668d08b543d024b4c8e4520905b178","tid":367484,"uid":52071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:24:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同緊老母食男朋友？</blockquote><br />\n牛都識上連登同煎扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e774147cd880ed2c427af0d94c9a3aeced36035","tid":367484,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:24:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔曳喎，外面少少燶仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都叫少少燶，咁正常燶係點，好撚燶又係點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85a6b98d4bb3a5846cc7bd4523a7b46305f3d80","tid":367484,"uid":110339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:25:49.000Z","msg":"第一次算好好啦"},{"pid":"626687d0b4aa4716f79f7ca3eae291692b2a948a","tid":367484,"uid":110339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:31:13.000Z","msg":"蒜頭拍大力d兩粒就得<br />\n同埋要足夠時間解凍(~30min)"},{"pid":"beb27314ab46e212d496dff0248cad20fa51f2d4","tid":367484,"uid":37089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T21:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次個火可以細返少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n煎牛扒Very hot pan係必需 大火先可以鎖住肉汁 一細火就會流晒出黎塊扒做拖鞋<br />\n<br />\n樓主下次用timer計時會比較可以控制好時間"},{"pid":"01706e0172dd43d7cc5a98136da8a1d662ce4404","tid":367484,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T22:03:20.000Z","msg":"幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1821a636568586c00e38e91c98a69a4ef70a0ba2","tid":367484,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得熟左啲<br />\n<br />\n始終認為每分鐘反，加埋4分鐘就夠"},{"pid":"c53fac0e8c458b7965ec5f02f0a554aeaf168c02","tid":367484,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗唔洗咁多蒜同香草呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實可以落鹽，但一落鹽完就要落鑊</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95352f305c0e5a705c426c48931d259cbf87cbfb","tid":367484,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次個火可以細返少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但唔係話要出煙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我煮煮下覺得唔對話先較細火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88db1110ce278dd374cd081a198ff4857e3f49ab","tid":367484,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:34:12.000Z","msg":"表面個色變到咁黑係因為放左黑椒<br />\n其實放小小海鹽即煎is ok<br />\n<br />\n應該分兩次煎<br />\n第一次用鉗小心細力夾住，中火先煎左個邊，鎖汁，每個位約半分鐘<br />\n<br />\n如果塊扒夠厚，即超過1蚊銀直徑的厚度，繼續中火平放煎到表面有血出，記得計時，再反另一邊，同樣時間<br />\n<br />\n最後再以大火煎，30秒為三成熟，1分鐘就五成，可放黑椒再煎<br />\n<br />\n當然厚度會有影響<br />\n<br />\n中火同大火煎之間，可起獲降溫4-5分鐘"},{"pid":"57e085f5ca135820a151e2c1d576b7d2859b4699","tid":367484,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗咁多蒜同香草呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實可以落鹽，但一落鹽完就要落鑊</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上youtube search la<br />\n可以yip 過夜架，你信佢...."},{"pid":"5ca9c7f2c5eed98d8baeb59a74cbb1647909dad3","tid":367484,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:38:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗咁多蒜同香草呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實可以落鹽，但一落鹽完就要落鑊</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上youtube search la<br />\n可以yip 過夜架，你信佢....</blockquote><br />\n薄扒先唔落鹽醃，厚嘅落一層厚厚嘅鹽，煎之前整走佢可以煎出好靚嘅面"},{"pid":"c97043ec8fe4f3160c50f56ca72934e39b64ea40","tid":367484,"uid":100099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:44:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗咁多蒜同香草呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實可以落鹽，但一落鹽完就要落鑊</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上youtube search la<br />\n可以yip 過夜架，你信佢....</blockquote><br />\n煎牛扒前會醃過夜真係第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebbee98f7623ea86465c3a3950187c51b2e62e0","tid":367484,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗咁多蒜同香草呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實可以落鹽，但一落鹽完就要落鑊</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上youtube search la<br />\n可以yip 過夜架，你信佢....</blockquote><br />\n煎牛扒前會醃過夜真係第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港式茶餐廳牛排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067297effd73eff27b3f58c507c889aab69efa61","tid":367484,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:48:01.000Z","msg":"大火每邊30秒   煎面<br />\n<br />\n之後轉中火  落牛油香草蒜"},{"pid":"9178dd1a112b18ff646c39cbd07caa6982928a07","tid":367484,"uid":60193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"&quot;因為同<span style=\"color: red;\">緊我老母食男朋友</span>唔敢玩電話所以影一張就無&quot;<br />\n<br />\n家明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bde4fcfb9c897f94811523831e96b96105375fd","tid":367484,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗咁多蒜同香草呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實可以落鹽，但一落鹽完就要落鑊</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上youtube search la<br />\n可以yip 過夜架，你信佢....</blockquote><br />\n煎牛扒前會醃過夜真係第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己睇la 𨳒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫你search 又唔search<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tingbistro/videos/805141176310093/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftingbistro%2Fvideos%2F805141176310093%2F&d=kPn1gkqpeMzuzWyn%2BST3LghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=562253dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tingbistro/videos/805141176310093/</a><br />\n1:25"},{"pid":"f3017e3771f77e7f4f3f8c0b4b3c8178d5009006","tid":367484,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗咁多蒜同香草呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實可以落鹽，但一落鹽完就要落鑊</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上youtube search la<br />\n可以yip 過夜架，你信佢....</blockquote><br />\n煎牛扒前會醃過夜真係第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港式茶餐廳牛排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3-4 mins<br />\n10-40mins<br />\n40mins or up 係對肉質有分別 utube大把videos講解<br />\n自己睇。"}]}